prj:TechnicalJustification.prj:justificationText:
We request the most compact ALMA configuration so as to not resolve out the CO emission; 
this would yield an angular resolution of 3.17 arcsecs at the redshifted CO 1-0 line 
frequency, corresponding to a spatial size of ~ 5.3 kpc at the GRB redshift of z=0.089.

We request the most compact ALMA configuration so as to not resolve out the CO emission; 
this would yield an angular resolution of 2.2 arcsecs at the CO line frequency, 
corresponding to a spatial extent of ~ 17 kpc at the GRB redshift of 0.584.

