this would yield an angular resolution of 2.64 arcsecs at the redshifted CO line frequency,
corresponding to a spatial extent of ~ 23 kpc at the GRB redshift of 1.496.

We request the most compact ALMA configuration so as to not resolve out the CO emission; 
this would yield an angular resolution of 3.22 arcsecs at the CO line frequency, 
corresponding to a spatial extent of ~ 27 kpc at the GRB redshift of 2.086.

We request the most compact ALMA configuration so as to not resolve out the CO emission; 
this would yield an angular resolution of 4.06 arcsecs at the CO line frequency, 
corresponding to a spatial extent of ~ 33 kpc at the GRB redshift of 2.452.
